OL,3,COscars 2025: Cinematographer scoops
OL,4,Cfirst Academy Award for 3hr 35m film
OL,6,FWelsh cinematographer Lol Crawley has
OL,7,Fdescribed his first ever Academy Award
OL,8,Fwin as 'overwhelming'.
OL,10,FCrawley, who grew up in Llansantffraid-
OL,11,Fym-Mechain in Powys, took home the
OL,12,Fbest cinematography gong for The
OL,13,FBrutalist.
OL,15,FDirected and co-written by Brady
OL,16,FCorbet, The Brutalist follows the
OL,17,Fstory of a Hungarian-Jewish architect
OL,18,Fwho is separated from his wife
OL,19,FErzsebet, played by Felicity Jones,
OL,20,Fand orphaned niece as he flees Nazi
OL,21,Fextermination to the US.
