OL,3,COscars 2025: Cinematographer scoops
OL,4,Cfirst Academy Award for 3hr 35m film
OL,6,FThe drama also secured the coveted
OL,7,Fbest actor award for Adrien Brody and
OL,8,Fbest original score.
OL,10,FAppearing on BBC Breakfast, the
OL,11,FWelshman reflected on his
OL,12,F'extraordinary' win and the 'long
OL,13,Fjourney' to success.
OL,15,FHe said: "It's wonderful and I really
OL,16,Fjust hope that, more than anything,
OL,17,Fall of this attention, accolades, and
OL,18,Falso the fact that people are seeing
OL,19,Fthe movie, that it's going to expand
OL,20,Fthe conversations about what cinema
OL,21,Fcan be."
