OL,3,COscars 2025: Cinematographer scoops
OL,4,Cfirst Academy Award for 3hr 35m film
OL,6,FThe 3 hour 35 minute-long film has a
OL,7,F15 minute intermission which Crawley
OL,8,Fdescribes as 'considered' and says he
OL,9,Ffeels like The Brutalist has "blown
OL,10,F(constraints) out the water".
OL,12,FOn accepting his award, Lol Crawley
OL,13,Fthanked the film's director, Brady
OL,14,FCorbet, "for recognising the richest
OL,15,Fdiamonds are always the hardest to
OL,16,Fmine and for standing by me if I ever
OL,17,Ffail to succeed."
OL,19,FHe also thanked "all my friends back
OL,20,Fin Wales".
