OL,6,FThe cinematographer, who studied his
OL,7,Fart in Wrexham, was just one of the
OL,8,FWelshmen recognised in last night's
OL,9,FAcademy Awards.
OL,11,FRhys Salcombe, from Aberystwyth, was
OL,12,Fpart of the visual effects team for
OL,13,Fscience fiction epic Dune: Part Two,
OL,14,Fstarring Timothee Chalamet and Zendaya.
OL,16,FBoth Salcombe and Crawley also
OL,17,Freceived BAFTAs in their respective
OL,18,Fcategories in the ceremony in London
OL,19,Fin February.
